OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FBy Politics Producer Maya Bowles
OL,9,FOn Wednesday 30 October, Chancellor
OL,10,FRachel Reeves will deliver her first
OL,11,FBudget.
OL,13,FIt marks a key moment for the new
OL,14,FLabour government, as Reeves tries to
OL,15,Fbalance the government's promises on
OL,16,Ftaxation with a commitment to keep
OL,17,Fborrowing under control and avoid a
OL,18,Freturn to austerity.
