OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FSince Labour won the election in July,
OL,8,Fgovernment ministers have repeatedly
OL,9,Ftalked about the #22 billion "black
OL,10,Fhole" in the public finances left by
OL,11,Fthe previous government.
OL,13,FBut last week the Institute for Fiscal
OL,14,FStudies warned that up to #25 billion
OL,15,Fin tax rises would be needed to
OL,16,Ffulfill Reeves' promise of "no return
OL,17,Fto austerity".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
