OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FRumours have been swirling about which
OL,8,Ftaxes the chancellor might choose to
OL,9,Fput up - with a focus particularly on
OL,10,Fa hike to employer National Insurance,
OL,11,Fwhich neither Reeves nor Prime
OL,12,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer have denied.
OL,14,FThe Labour manifesto promised not to
OL,15,Fraise taxes for "working people",
OL,16,Fruling out a rise in National
OL,17,FInsurance, income tax and VAT.
OL,19,FBut which other taxes rises could be
OL,20,Fannounced ?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
