OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FEmployer National Insurance
OL,9,FThe main focus of Budget speculation
OL,10,Fhas been on employer National
OL,11,FInsurance contributions, as the PM and
OL,12,Fchancellor have both signaled a hike
OL,13,Fis on the cards.
OL,15,FThe key question is whether this would
OL,16,Fbreak Labour's manifesto promise not
OL,17,Fto raise taxes for "working people".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
