OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FThe PM has suggested it wouldn't, but
OL,8,Fbusiness groups say an increase in
OL,9,Femployer NI would be a "clear
OL,10,Fmanifesto breach", placing "an
OL,11,Fadditional strain on businesses".
OL,13,FThey argue a rise would impact working
OL,14,Fpeople as employers could restrict new
OL,15,Fhires, limit pay rises, scale back
OL,16,Fpension payments or even put up prices
OL,17,Ffor customers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
