OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies
OL,8,Fcalculate introducing NI on employer
OL,9,Fpension contributions could raise
OL,10,Faround #17bn per year if taxed at the
OL,11,Fsame 13.8% rate as normal employer NI
OL,12,Fcontributions.
OL,14,FThe PM and Reeves have not ruled out
OL,15,Fthis option either.
