OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FIt's the tax levied on any profit when
OL,8,Fsomeone sells an asset worth more than
OL,9,F#6,000 - like a second home, or shares.
OL,11,FThe CGT rate is 10% for profits above
OL,12,F#3,000, or 18% on profits from selling
OL,13,Fa residential property other than a
OL,14,Fmain home.
OL,16,FThe higher rate of CGT is 24% on
OL,17,Fresidential property and 20% on all
OL,18,Fother chargeable assets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
