OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FThere had been speculation of an
OL,8,Fincrease to 39% for the higher rate,
OL,9,Fwhich the PM described as "wide of the
OL,10,Fmark" in an interview with Bloomberg
OL,11,Fon Monday.
OL,13,FCGT raises around #15bn a year,
OL,14,Faccording to the IFS. Estimates by HM
OL,15,FRevenue and Customs show a 1
OL,16,Fpercentage point increase in the
OL,17,Fhigher rates of capital gains tax
OL,18,Fwould raise #100 million in 2027-28.
