OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FCorporation tax is paid by UK
OL,8,Fcompanies on the annual profits a
OL,9,Fcompany makes - the current main rate
OL,10,Fis 25%.
OL,12,FRachel Reeves confirmed during her
OL,13,Fspeech at the government's
OL,14,FInternational Investment Summit on
OL,15,FMonday that she will cap corporation
OL,16,Ftax at 25% for the rest of the
OL,17,Fparliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
