OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,F"At the budget, this government will
OL,8,Fbe outlining a corporate tax roadmap.
OL,9,FWe will cap the rate of corporation
OL,10,Ftax at 25 per cent, the lowest in the
OL,11,FG7, for the duration of this
OL,12,Fparliament", she told business leaders.
OL,14,FInheritance tax
OL,16,FInheritance tax is paid on someone's
OL,17,Festate when they die - it includes
OL,18,Ftheir property and other assets, but
OL,19,Fnot if the value is below #325,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
