OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FIt's currently taxed at 40%, but only
OL,8,Fon the part of the estate above the
OL,9,Fthreshold.
OL,11,FThe number of people who pay
OL,12,Finheritance tax is very small - last
OL,13,Fyear only 5% of estates were charged
OL,14,Fan inheritance tax bill, and there are
OL,15,Falso quite a lot of exemptions.
OL,17,FA number of organisations have called
OL,18,Fon the chancellor to reform
OL,19,Finheritance tax in order to get rid of
OL,20,Fsome of the loopholes.
