OL,3,CNI, capital gains, corporation tax:
OL,4,CWhat could we expect from Reeves'
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FThe think tank Demos have suggested a
OL,8,Fnew banded inheritance tax system,
OL,9,Furging Reeves to cut the amount for
OL,10,Fless valuable estates and increase it
OL,11,Ffor the wealthier ones.
OL,13,FFuel duty on standard petrol and
OL,14,Fdiesel is currently 52.95p per litre,
OL,15,Fafter the Conservatives cut it by 5p
OL,16,Fin 2022.
OL,18,FIt's expected to raise #24.7 billion
OL,19,Fin 2023-2024 according for the Office
OL,20,Ffor Budget Responsibility.
